    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-fresh condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero paint chips or swirl marks, protected by a premium ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin retains its original 'new car' scent; the leather upholstery is supple and free of any creasing or wear. Every button, switch, and feature operates with factory precision. Mechanically, it is flawless, accompanied by a comprehensive service portfolio documenting every scheduled maintenance performed by certified technicians. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to own a turn-key masterpiece that drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
