    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, maintained in pristine, showroom-ready condition. This vehicle reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the secondary market, featuring an impeccable exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory luster. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been rigorously vetted to ensure it meets the requirements of the most discerning collector. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a motorcar of distinguished caliber and uncompromising quality.",
