      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly spectacular shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered since day one, always kept tucked away in the garage, and is looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. You really have to see it in person to believe how spotless it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014let's get you behind the wheel!",
