      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in collector-quality condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through its high-pressure VANOS system and six individual throttle bodies. The chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement and a fresh rod bearing service. Power is managed via a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal lateral grip. Finished in original paint with zero orange peel and a pristine interior, this vehicle maintains its factory-spec suspension kinematics and throttle response. A mechanically synchronized, turn-key example for the discerning purist.",
